], 'source': 'https://armyinform.com.ua/2023/04/19/u-bahmuti-vorog-atakuye-malymy-grupamy-ta-vstupaye-v-kontaktni-strileczki-boyi-polkovnyk-dmytro-zavorotnyuk/'}